refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public Vtiful\Kernel\Table Vtiful\Kernel\Table::columns arraycolumns
Defines the columns of the table. Any previously defined columns are replaced.

&reftitle.parameters;


  columns

   An array of column definitions. Each entry is an associative array that may contain the keys header (string), formula (string), total_string (string), total_function (int), total_value (float), format (a Vtiful\Kernel\Format instance or format resource) and header_format (a Vtiful\Kernel\Format instance or format resource).
